M by more than an order of\nmagnitude from the current values. Although the survey strategies presented\nhere have not been fully optimized, these initial investigations are an\nimportant step in the development of the final hardware design and\nimplementation of the WFIRST mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2017 18:53:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 20:34:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-25"}
